metadata.name: Ethereal Archangel
metadata.description: I prompted Midjourney for a pre-Raphaelite ethereal female archangel warrior with armor. I received this stunner during the beta test on Aug. 23, 2022, when Midjourney was testing a new algorithm for 24 hours. The upscale had problems with the eyes and nose, which I improved by hand in Photoshop. Image of a bare chested angel with feathered wings, long dark hair, and a serious expression.
